		<title>New California Traffic Laws for 2021 &#124; What Drivers Should Know To Avoid A Traffic Ticket</title>
		<link>https://www.ticketclinic.com/blog/new-california-traffic-laws-for-2021-what-drivers-should-know-to-avoid-a-traffic-ticket</link>
