		<title>DUI FAQ: Does Mouthwash Affect a Breathalyzer Test?</title>
		<link>https://www.ticketclinic.com/blog/dui-faq-does-mouthwash-affect-a-breathalyzer-test</link>
				<comments>https://www.ticketclinic.com/blog/dui-faq-does-mouthwash-affect-a-breathalyzer-test#respond</comments>
